Yawan adadin cututtukan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen EU/EUA da Ingila wanda ke tabbatar da cewa cutar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe, yana faruwa a matakai daban -daban dangane da ƙasar.
