A ranar 9 ga Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka, China ta ba da rahoton cewa an gano cutar coronavirus, wanda yanzu ake kira mai saurin kamuwa da cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta haifar an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaidar da aka samu zuwa yau ita ce kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya mai laushi, wato, kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar nimoniya ba kuma yawancin su sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari, COVID-19 ya ci gaba zuwa wani mummunan yanayin da ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari ke da mummunan yanayin da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin karuwar cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU / EEA) da Ingila (UK) kuma mun kwatanta shi da lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin adadin COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin EU/EEA da UK da Italiya a lokacin Janairu 31 - Maris 15, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya kara fadada yanayin ƙasa kuma a halin yanzu, ayyukan cutar COVID-19 a sauran ƙasashen duniya sun wuce wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar EuroSurveillance ta 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri et al. ya ba da rahoton farkon shari'ar COVID-19 da aka tabbatar a Turai kamar yadda WHO ta bayyana.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon lamuran uku da aka tabbatar a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020.
Zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, an samu shari'o'in COVID-19 a dukkan ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da Ingila (UK), tare da 17,750 shari'o'i da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai, tare da 39,768 shari'o'i da mutuwar 1,727 da aka ruwaito tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da wannan kwanan wata.
Samun adadi mai yawa na shari'ar COVID-19 da kuma yaduwar tarawa
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta ƙididdigar shari'ar COVID-19 da aka ruwaito daga kowace ƙasa a duniya a kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe daga tushen hukuma kawai kamar su Ma'aikatun Kiwon Lafiya na ƙasashe, Hukumomin Kiwon Lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK da kuma kwatanta shi da cutar a Italiya.
A matsayin wakilin yaduwar shari'o'in COVID-19 masu aiki, mun lissafa taƙaitaccen yaduwar kwanaki 14 na shari'o'in COVID-19 yayin da muke la'akari da yanayin yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya a lokacin Janairu 1 - 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma nuna adadin adadin adadin wadanda aka ruwaito a kowace kasa har zuwa karfe 8:00 na safiyar 15 ga Maris, 2020 a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020 idan aka kwatanta da Italiya.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Yanayin taƙaitaccen tarihin kwanaki 14 na yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya yana bin lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da duk Burtaniya, yawan cutar COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ya karu sosai a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (abun da ke ciki).
Wannan ya kasance ne saboda karuwar yawan adadin wadanda aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da UK sun ga irin wannan karuwar karuwar cutar ta COVID-19.
Figure 2 ya nuna yawan adadin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da Italiya a cikin lokacin Janairu 31 - Maris 15, 2020.
Wannan ya nuna musamman cewa a ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe, sauran ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da UK sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin shari'o'in da za a iya kwatanta da na Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin rahotannin COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Yanayin da aka gani a cikin yawan cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa kasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance a cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, da yiwuwar bambancin ma'anar shari'ar a cikin ƙasashe da kuma ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda ya kamata a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da kamawa da gwaji.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya sun ba da rahoton halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10% na marasa lafiyar COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da raka'a masu kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da asibiti da / ko asibiti na kula da kulawa mai tsanani na COVID-19 a halin yanzu ana samun su ne kawai a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i, bi da bi (ba a nuna alkaluma ba).
Koyaya, yakamata a tattara su ta hanyar tsari don haɓaka bayanan sa ido na yanzu waɗanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin rahotannin da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a 2010-11 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai tsakanin yawan gadaje masu kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a Portugal a kan mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (gadoji 12.5 na kulawa mai tsanani da na tsaka - tsaka a cikin 100,000 na yawan jama'a a 2010-11).
Yada yawan asibitocin COVID-19 da ke cikin asibiti da ke da alaƙa da haɗarin 90% na ƙarfin gado mai mahimmanci tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da UK An ba da kwatancen yanayin da ya shafi yanayin ƙoshin lafiya tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da UK a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ECDC na Babban Hadarin Hadarin Hasara akan COVID-19.
Tunda har yanzu akwai lokuta da yawa a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da wasu yankuna na Burtaniya kuma asibitoci da raka'a masu kulawa da hankali suna ba da sabis ga yawan jama'ar yanki, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da shari'o'i da gadajen kulawa da hankali a matakin farko a cikin Nomenclature of Territorial Unit for Statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar da aka samu daga Italiya da kuma yanayin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da hankali ya kamata su shirya kansu don yanayin ci gaba da yaduwar al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 da karuwar yawan marasa lafiyar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani kamar yadda yake faruwa a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon kimantawa na ECDC, tare da sauya ra'ayi daga iyakancewa zuwa ragewa, ana buƙatar saurin, mai saurin aiki da kuma cikakkiyar hanyar rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, saboda idan ba a aiwatar da shi a kan lokaci ba, yanke shawara mai sauri da ake tsammani a cikin adadin shari'o'in na iya ba da isasshen lokaci ga masu haɓaka da asibitoci don fahimta, karɓa da kuma daidaita amsar su daidai.
Har ila yau, kimantawa mai haɗari yana lissafin matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don magance tasirin cutar.
Kasashe suna da karancin damar kara kokarin sarrafa su da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2.
Idan hakan ta gaza, akwai yiwuwar tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA zai fuskanci karuwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) da ke haifar da mummunan ciwon numfashi (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ya kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ya kamu da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda hakan ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar kwayar cutar SARS-CoV, wacce ta haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama daga jemage kuma yana haifar da irin wannan alamun ta hanyar aiki iri ɗaya.
Ko da yake COVID-19 yana da ƙananan tsanani da mutuwar fiye da SARS, amma yana da saurin yaduwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
