Hakanan, an kuma nuna mahimmancin buƙatar maye gurbin abubuwan gina jiki cikin nasara da kuma tasirin ci gaban kwayar cutar a hankali kan tsananin cutar.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) suna cikin dangin Coronaviridae wanda ya ƙunshi ƙungiyoyin ƙwayoyin cuta masu ƙarancin ƙwayoyin cuta, masu ƙarancin ƙwayoyin RNA guda ɗaya.
Waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta, waɗanda ke ɗaukar mafi girman ƙwayoyin cuta na 26 zuwa 32 kilobases a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA, an ba su suna CoVs saboda ƙirar su kamar kambi a ƙarƙashin microscope na lantarki.
A tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halittar da ba su da sashi wanda ke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin halitta suna da manyan sigogi guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda aka canza zuwa pp1a da pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Ana sarrafa polyprotein don samar da furotin 16 marasa tsari da ake kira nsp1 ~ 16.
Sauran ɓangaren kwayoyin halitta suna da ORFs don gina jiki, ciki har da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) da nucleoproteins (N).
Hakanan ana tsara furotin masu taimako da yawa na musamman na CoVs ta hanyar al'adun CoVs daban -daban.
Dangane da bambancin jerin sunayen sunadarai, an rarraba CoV zuwa ƙarni huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, da delta-CoV), daga cikinsu beta-CoVs sune mafi yawan HCoVs kuma an raba su zuwa zuriya huɗu (A, B, C, da D).
Shaidar ethnographic ta nuna cewa dodanni da ƙudaje sune tushen kwayoyin halittar alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune manyan ƙwayoyin gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A cikin dubunnan shekaru, CoVs sun ci gaba da ƙetare shingen jinsuna kuma sun fito a matsayin wasu mahimman cututtukan ɗan adam.
Zuwa yau, an san mutane bakwai da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HCoV.
