A watan Disamba na 2019, an sami barkewar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda yanzu aka sake masa suna zuwa cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sake masa suna zuwa cutar mai saurin kamuwa da cutar coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
