Amsoshin ƙasa sun haɗa da matakan keɓewa kamar keɓewa (wanda aka sani da umarnin zama a gida, umarnin mafaka a wurinka, ko kullewa). Ya zuwa 2 ga Afrilu, kusan mutane miliyan 300 a Amurka ko kusan kashi 90% na yawan jama'a suna cikin wasu nau'ikan kullewa, sama da mutane miliyan 50 a Philippines suna cikin kullewa, kusan mutane miliyan 59 a Afirka ta Kudu suna cikin kullewa, kuma mutane biliyan 1.3 a Indiya suna cikin kullewa.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, mutane biliyan 1.7 a duniya suna cikin wasu nau'ikan kulle-kulle, wanda ya karu zuwa mutane biliyan 2.6 bayan kwana biyu - kusan kashi ɗaya bisa uku na yawan mutanen duniya.
An gano farkon yanayin tabbatar da COVID-19 a Wuhan a ranar 1 ga Disamba, 2019; wani rahoto da ba a tabbatar da shi ba ya nuna cewa farkon lamarin ya faru ne a ranar 17 ga Nuwamba.
Likita Zhang Jixian ya lura da tarin cututtukan cutar nimoniya da ba a san dalilin da ya sa ba a ranar 26 ga Disamba, bayan asibitin sa ya sanar da Wuhan Jiangnan CDC a ranar 27 ga Disamba.
Gwajin farko na kwayoyin halittar samfurin mai haƙuri a ranar 27 ga Disamba, 2019 ya nuna kasancewar kwayar cutar coronavirus mai kama da SARS.
Hukumar Kiwon Lafiyar Birnin Wuhan ta ba da sanarwar jama'a a ranar 31 ga Disamba.
An sanar da WHO a ranar.
