An bayyana shi a matsayin "garkuwa mafi girma a tarihin ɗan adam", an ba da sanarwar yankin kewayewa don hana motsi a Wuhan a ranar 23 ga Janairu, wanda aka faɗaɗa zuwa birane 15 a Hubei, wanda ya shafi mutane miliyan 57 gaba ɗaya.
An haramta amfani da motocin mutane a cikin garin.
An soke bukukuwan sabuwar shekara ta kasar Sin (Janairu 25) a wurare da dama.
Hukumomi sun kuma sanar da gina asibitin wucin gadi, asibitin Hoshensen, wanda aka kammala a cikin kwanaki 10.
Daga baya an gina wani asibiti, asibitin Leichensson, don kula da ƙarin marasa lafiya.
Baya ga sabbin asibitocin da aka gina, kasar Sin ta kuma mayar da wasu wurare 14 a Wuhan kamar cibiyoyin taro da filayen wasa zuwa asibitoci na wucin gadi.A ranar 26 ga Janairu, gwamnati ta kafa karin matakan dakile barkewar COVID-19, ciki har da bayar da sanarwar kiwon lafiya ga matafiya da kuma tsawaita hutun bikin bazara.
An kuma rufe jami'o'i da makarantu a duk fadin kasar.
