An tabbatar da yaduwar COVID-19 daga China zuwa Koriya ta Kudu a ranar 20 ga Janairun 2020.
Hukumar kiwon lafiya ta kasar ta rubuta wani karuwa mai ban mamaki a cikin shari'o'in da aka tabbatar a ranar 20 ga Fabrairu, wanda ya danganci taron jama'a a Daigu na wani sabon motsi na addini da aka fi sani da Cocin Shincheonji na Yesu.
Masu bautar Shincheon da suka zo Daegu daga Wuhan sun yi shakkar asalin cutar.
A ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, 1,261 ko kusan 13% na mabiyan Cocin 9,336 sun ba da rahoton bayyanar cututtuka.
A ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu, an samu karin mutane 2,000 da suka kamu da cutar a Koriya, wanda ya karu zuwa 3,150 a ranar 29 ga watan Fabrairu.
An killace dukkan sansanonin sojin Koriya ta Kudu bayan da gwaje -gwaje suka tabbatar da cewa sojoji uku sun kamu da cutar.
Shirye-shiryen jiragen sama ma sun sami matsala kuma saboda haka an canza su. Shirin da Koriya ta Kudu ta gabatar shine mafi girma kuma mafi kyawun tsari a duniya don bincika yawan jama'a don cutar da kuma ware duk waɗanda ke da cutar, gami da ganowa da keɓe waɗanda suka tuntube su.
Hanyoyin tantancewa sun hada da tilasta kai-da-kai na alamun cututtuka ta hanyar sabbin masu shigowa na duniya ta hanyar aikace-aikacen wayar hannu, saurin gwaji don kwayar cutar tare da sakamakon da ke samuwa a washegari, da haɓaka ƙarfin gwaji don gwada mutane 20,000 kowace rana.
Ana ganin shirin Koriya ta Kudu a matsayin nasara wajen shawo kan barkewar cutar duk da cewa ba a killace dukkan biranen ba. Da farko dai al'ummar Koriya ta Kudu sun rabu biyu kan yadda Shugaba Moon Jae-in ya mayar da martani kan rikicin.
Yawancin 'yan Koriya sun sanya hannu kan takardun da ke kira da a tsige Moon, suna zargin gwamnatin ta yi mummunan aiki da barkewar cutar, ko kuma sun yaba da yadda ta amsa.
