A ranar 29 ga Maris, an sanar da cewa daga ranar 1 ga Afrilu, duk sabbin masu shigowa daga ƙasashen waje za a killace su na makonni biyu.
A cewar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai a ranar 1 ga Afrilu, Koriya ta Kudu ta sami buƙatun taimako na gwaji daga ƙasashe 121 daban -daban.
Iran ta ba da rahoton lamuranta na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Qom a ranar 19 ga Fabrairu, inda mutane biyu suka mutu a ranar, a cewar ma'aikatar lafiya da ilimin likitanci.
Matakan farko da gwamnatin ta sanar sun hada da rufe kide kide da sauran al'adu, wasanni, da sallar Juma'a, da rufe jami'o'i, cibiyoyin ilimi da makarantu.
Iran ta ware Riyal tiriliyan biyar don magance cutar.
Shugaba Hassan Rouhani ya ce a ranar 26 ga Fabrairun 2020 cewa babu wani shiri na killace yankunan da cutar ta shafa kuma za a killace mutane ne kawai.
