WHO ta yaba da kokarin da hukumomin kasar Sin ke yi wajen gudanar da yaduwar cutar.
WHO ta yi nuni da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS ta 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da yin sirri wanda ya kawo cikas ga kokarin hanawa da kuma kawar da cutar, da kuma rikicin yanzu inda gwamnatin tsakiya ta "ba da sabuntawa akai-akai don kauce wa tsoro kafin hutun sabuwar shekara ta Lunar".
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, a mayar da martani ga shawarar da hukumomin tsakiya suka yanke na sanya dokar hana zirga-zirga a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Gallia ya yi sharhi cewa yayin da "ba a ba da shawarar WHO ba" wannan "alamu ne masu matukar muhimmanci na jajircewar hana barkewar cutar a inda ta fi mayar da hankali" kuma ya kira ta "marasa misali a tarihin kiwon lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta damuwar kasa da kasa (PHEIC), wanda shine PHEIC na shida tun lokacin da aka fara daukar matakan a lokacin annobar cutar ta 2009 ta alade.
Darakta Janar na WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce PHEIC ya haifar da "hadarin yaduwar duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi ba tare da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya ba.
A cikin martani game da aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili da zai sa a dauki irin waɗannan matakan da za su tsoma baki ba tare da bukatar tafiya da kasuwanci ba" kuma "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar ƙuntata kasuwanci da motsi ba".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su bada gudummawar dala miliyan 675 don shirye-shiryen dabaru a kasashe masu karamin karfi, suna mai cewa akwai bukatar taimakawa kasashen da "ba su da tsarin da za su gano mutanen da ke dauke da kwayar cutar, ko da kuwa tana kan tasowa".
Tedros ya ci gaba da bayyanawa a cikin wasu kalamai, cewa "mu ne kawai muke da ƙarfi kamar yadda mafi rauni ke da ƙarfi" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya da su "sa hannun jari a yau ko kuma su biya ƙarin daga baya". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta kafa COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar a wani taron manema labarai.
A wannan rana, Tedros ya ce Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Antonio Guterres ya amince da "ba da ƙarfin tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya gaba ɗaya a cikin martani".
Sakamakon haka an kunna wata kungiyar kula da rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wacce ta daidaita martani na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda a cewar WHO zai basu damar "mai da hankali kan martanin kiwon lafiya, yayin da sauran hukumomin za su iya amfani da kwarewarsu wajen magance manyan matsalolin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki da ci gaban barkewar cutar".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an tura wata ƙungiyar haɗin gwiwa ta WHO tare da China don ziyarci yankin don ba da ƙwarewar ƙasa ga ƙwararrun ƙasashen duniya da WHO a China, don taimakawa cikin gudanar da gida da kuma shirya bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin ƙasa don tantance "tsananin cutar da kamuwa da cuta" da kuma kimanta "tasirin ayyukan amsawa a matakin lardi da na gunduma, gami da birane da yankuna.
A sakamakon barkewar cutar a Iran, WHO ta tura wata kungiyar hadin gwiwa don tantance lamarin. A ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu, hukumomin WHO sun ce za a tantance barazanar coronavirus a duniya daga "mai girma" zuwa "mai matukar girma", wanda shine matakin tsaro da kimanta hadarin.
Mike Ryan, darektan zartarwa na shirin gaggawa na lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadin a cikin wata sanarwa cewa "wannan gwaji ne na gaskiya ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: lokaci ya yi da za a farka.
Wannan kwayar cutar na iya zuwa kuma kuna buƙatar kasancewa cikin shiri, "yana mai cewa matakan da suka dace na iya taimakawa duniya ta guje wa" mafi munin yanayin ta. "
Ryan ya ci gaba da cewa, alkaluman da ake da su yanzu ba su tabbatar da hukumomin kiwon lafiya na duniya da su ayyana cutar a duniya ba, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwar za ta nuna cewa "muna da tabbacin cewa kowane dan Adam a duniya zai kamu da cutar".
A ranar 11 ga Maris, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
Darakta Janar ya ce WHO "ta damu matuka da yadda ake samun yaduwar cutar da kuma yadda ake fama da cutar da kuma yadda ake fama da rashin aiki". WHO ta fuskanci babban suka a matsayin rashin kula da cutar, gami da jinkirin ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya da kuma rarraba kwayar cutar a matsayin annoba.
Wannan takarda ta kunshi takardar neman murabus din Darakta Janar na WHO, Tedros Adhanom, wanda mutane 733,000 suka sanya hannu a ranar 6 ga watan Afrilu.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, wasu kwararru na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kan kare hakkin dan adam sun yi kira ga girmama hakkin kowa a lokacin annobar COVID-19.
Kwararru sun ce kowa ya cancanci sa baki don ceton rayuka kuma wannan alhakin na gwamnati ne.
Kungiyar ta jaddada cewa bai kamata a taba amfani da karancin albarkatu ko inshorar lafiya a matsayin hujjar nuna bambanci ga wata kungiya ba.
Masana sun jaddada cewa kowane mutum, gami da nakasassu, kungiyoyin 'yan tsiraru, tsofaffi, mutanen da aka kwashe cikin gida, marasa gida, mutanen da ke rayuwa cikin mawuyacin hali, mutanen da ke zaune a cikin keɓewa, da kuma 'yan gudun hijira da sauran kungiyoyin da ba a kayyade ba waɗanda ke buƙatar taimakon gwamnati, suna da' yancin samun lafiya.
Kungiyoyin gwamnati na kasa da kasa suna magance tasirin tattalin arziki da zamantakewar rikicin COVID-19.
Kungiyar hadin gwiwar tattalin arziki da ci gaba ta kafa wani dandamali don samar da cikakken bayani da kuma ra'ayoyi da shawarwari kan martani kan manufofi a cikin kasashen duniya.
Daga manufofi zuwa ƙarfafa tsarin kiwon lafiya da tattalin arzikin duniya zuwa magance tasirin hanawa da ƙuntatawa kan balaguro, cibiyar dijital ta ƙunshi mai bin diddigin manufofin ƙasa, kuma an yi niyyar taimaka wa ƙasashe su koya daga juna da sauƙaƙe daidaitaccen martani na duniya ga ƙalubalen coronavirus.
Ministan Amurka, Michael Gove, ministan Burtaniya don ofishin majalisar ministoci, da kuma Eduardo Bolsonaro, dan Shugaba Jair Bolsonaro na Brazil, sun soki gwamnatin China kan yadda ta magance cutar da ta fara a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
An kori wasu gwamnoni na jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin (CPC) a lardin domin magance kokarin killace mutane a tsakiyar kasar Sin, a matsayin wata alama ta rashin jin dadin yadda kungiyar siyasa ta mayar da martani ga barkewar cutar a yankunan.
