Wasu jami'an kasar Sin, kamar Zhao Lijian sun yi watsi da yarda da cutar coronavirus da ta barke a Wuhan, suna goyon bayan jita-jita game da COVID-19 da ta samo asali daga Amurka ko Italiya.
Gwamnatin Amurka ta Donald Trump ta kira coronavirus "Cinema Virus" ko "Wuhan Virus", tana mai cewa "Tsarin sarrafawa na China ya juya kwayar cutar zuwa annobar duniya yanzu", wanda wasu masu sukar suka yi la'akari da wariyar launin fata da "rashin nasarar gwamnatinsa wajen dakile cutar".
Jaridar Daily Beast ta samu wata wayar gwamnatin Amurka da ke nuna cewa an yi amfani da hanyoyin sadarwa a cikin Majalisar Tsaro ta kasa, tare da ambaton dabarun cewa "dukkanin China ne".
Ana tambayarmu mu yi kokarin isar da wannan sakon ta kowace hanya, gami da taron manema labarai da kuma halartar talabijin. "Kasuwanci kamar Politico, Foreign Policy da Bloomberg sun yi iƙirarin cewa ƙoƙarin da China ke yi na aika taimako ga ƙasashen da ke fama da cutar wani ɓangare ne na farfaganda don haɓaka tasirin duniya.
Shugaban harkokin wajen EU, Josep Borrell ya yi gargadin cewa akwai "wani bangare na siyasa wanda ya hada da gwagwarmayar samun tasiri ta hanyar sauyawa da kuma 'siyasa ta sassaucin ra'ayi.'"
Borel ya kuma ce "China tana ta kai hare-hare ta hanyar isar da sakon cewa, sabanin Amurka, ita abokiyar zama ce mai alhakin abin dogaro".
Kasar Sin ta kuma yi kira ga Amurka da ta dage takunkumin da ta kakaba wa kasashen Syria, Venezuela da Iran, wadanda ake zargin sun ba da tallafi ga kasashen biyu.
An toshe kyautar Jack Ma na masks 100,000 zuwa Cuba a ranar 3 ga Afrilu ta takunkumin Amurka.
Har ila yau, an zargi hukumomin Amurka da karkatar da tallafin da ake nufi ga wasu ƙasashe zuwa ƙasarsu.
