"China ce kawai ta mayar da martani ta hanyar biyu", in ji jakadan Italiya a EU Maurizio Massari.
Hakika, wannan ba alama ce mai kyau ba ta haɗin kan Turai".
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, bayan kiran waya da Firayim Ministan Italiya Giuseppe Conte, Shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin ya shirya wa sojojin Rasha tura likitocin soja, motocin kashe kwayoyin cuta na musamman da sauran kayan aikin likita.
Jaridar La Stampa ta Italiya ta kawo wani "manyan majiyoyin siyasa" da ba a bayyana sunansu ba, inda ta ce kashi 80 cikin dari na taimakon da Rasha ta bayar "ba shi da amfani ko kuma ba shi da amfani ga Italiya".
Majiyar ta zargi Rasha da yin "ciniki da diplomasiyya".
