Hakanan an sami yanayin cin kasuwa mai saurin tsoro a yankuna da yawa, wanda ya haifar da karancin kayan masarufi kamar abinci, takarda na bayan gida, da ruwan kwalba daga kan ɗakunan ajiya, wanda ya rage wadata.
Musamman masana'antar fasaha an yi musu gargadi game da jinkirin jigilar kayan lantarki.
