Baya ga abubuwan da ke ba da danshi da kare fata, ƙwararrun ƙirar na iya ƙunsar acid a matsayin mai daidaita pH (acetic acid, ascorbic acid, lactic acid), benzoic acid mai aiki da ƙwayoyin cuta da sauran masu haɓaka fata (aloe vera, bitamin, menthol, tsire-tsire masu tsire-tsire). Wani bincike mai zurfi daga Jami'ar Oregon School of Public Health ya nuna cewa sabulu mai tsabta, trichloroquine, yana da tasiri kamar sabulu mai amfani da maganin ƙwayoyin cuta na masu amfani da su.
