Mai tsabtace hannu ko mai tsabtace hannu shine mai tsabtace hannu tare da tushen ruwa.
A ƙarshen shekarun 1990s da farkon karni na 21, masu tsabtace hannu marasa ruwa na ruwa (wanda aka fi sani da rubs na hannu, rubs na hannu ko masu tsabtace hannu) sun fara samun karbuwa.
Yawancin waɗannan suna dogara ne akan isopropyl barasa ko ethanol, waɗanda aka tsara tare da carbomer (polymer na acrylic acid) a cikin gel a cikin mai kara kuzari, ko glycerin a cikin ruwa ko kumfa kamar moisturizer, don sauƙin amfani da rage tasirin bushewar barasa.
Haɗin hydrogen-peroxide yana ƙara haɓaka aikin rigakafin ƙwayoyin cuta. Sanitizers na hannu masu amfani da giya 60 zuwa 95% suna da ingancin kashe ƙwayoyin cuta.
Alcohol rub sanitizers suna kashe kwayoyin cuta, kwayoyin cuta masu jurewa da magunguna (MRSA da VRE), tarin fuka da wasu ƙwayoyin cuta (gami da HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, mura da hepatitis) da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta.
Alcohol rub sanitizers dauke da kashi 70% na barasa, suna kashe kwayoyin 99.97% bayan dakika 30 na amfani (ƙarancin 3.5 log, daidai da raguwar decibel 35) kuma suna kashe kwayoyin 99.99% zuwa 99.999% bayan minti 1 na amfani (ƙarancin 4 zuwa 5 log).
Sanitizers na hannu masu amfani da giya kusan ba su da tasiri ga nau'in kwayar cutar norovirus (ko Norwalk) wanda shine mafi yawan sanadin cututtukan gastrointestinal. Ya kamata a yi amfani da isasshen mai tsabtace hannu ko ruwan sha don rufe duka hannuwan biyu ko kuma rufe su gaba ɗaya.
Ana shafawa gaba da baya na hannaye biyu da tsakiyar da yatsun yatsunsu na kusan dakika 30, har sai ruwan, kumfa ko gel ya bushe.
Dole ne a wanke yatsun hannu sosai ta hanyar shafawa a cikin dabino biyu. Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amurka ta ba da shawarar wanke hannu maimakon rubs na tsabtace hannu, musamman idan hannayen suna da datti.
Ana amfani da waɗannan magungunan don sauƙaƙe amfani da su da kuma saurin kashe ƙwayoyin cuta; duk da haka, bai kamata a yi amfani da su azaman maye gurbin wanke hannu ba idan sabulu da ruwa ba su da shi.
Amfani da tsabtace hannu na giya sau da yawa na iya haifar da bushewar fata sai dai idan an haɗa man shafawa da / ko moisturizer na fata a cikin tsari.
Za a iya rage ko kawar da tasirin bushewar giya ta hanyar hada glycerin da / ko wasu lubricants a cikin tsari.
A cikin gwajin asibiti, maganin wanke hannu mai dauke da barasa wanda ke dauke da man shafawa ya rage yawan zafin jiki da bushewar fata idan aka kwatanta da sabulu ko kayan shafawa.
Abun da ke haifar da rashin lafiyar haɗuwa da giya ko abubuwan da ke cikin rubs na hannu suna da cututtukan fata, haɗuwa da cututtukan urticaria ko kuma rashin lafiyan.
