Aikace-aikacen COVID-19 aikace-aikacen software ne na wayar hannu waɗanda aka tsara don taimakawa a cikin ganowa, watau aiwatar da gano mutane ("liƙan) waɗanda ƙila sun kasance cikin hulɗa da mai cutar a cikin martani ga cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20.
An haɓaka ko kuma an ba da shawarar aikace -aikace da yawa tare da tallafin gwamnati a wasu yankuna da yankuna.
An samar da tsarin da yawa don gina aikace -aikacen gano lamba.
An tayar da damuwa game da sirri, musamman game da tsarin da ke dogara da bin diddigin yanayin masu amfani da app.
A cikin zaɓi na ɗan gajeren lokaci, yana haɗa da amfani da siginar Bluetooth don yin rajistar kusanci da mai amfani da sauran wayoyin salula.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple sun ba da sanarwar cewa za su haɗa aikin kai tsaye cikin tsarin aiki na Android da iOS don tallafawa irin waɗannan ƙa'idodin tushen Bluetooth.
A China, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da wata manhaja tare da Alipay, wanda zai baiwa 'yan kasa damar duba ko sun kasance tare da mutanen da ke da COVID-19.
Ana amfani da shi a birane sama da 200 na kasar Sin. A Singapore, ana amfani da wata manhaja mai suna TraceTogether.
An kirkiro manhajar ne ta hanyar al'ummar IT ta gida, an sake ta a matsayin buɗaɗɗen tushe kuma za a ba da ita ga gwamnati. Arewacin Macedonia ta ƙaddamar da wata manhajar da ke da tushen Bluetooth "StopKorona!" don gano hulɗa tare da mutanen da ke da yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar da kuma ba da saurin amsa ga hukumomin kiwon lafiya.
Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha da Ma'aikatar Lafiya ne suka kirkiro manhajar.
Har zuwa 14 ga Afrilu, 2020, wannan app ɗin yana jiran amincewa daga Google Play Store da Apple App Store.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnati ta ce manhajar gano lamba tana cikin wani mataki na ci gaba, kuma za ta kasance a shirye don tsarawa a cikin makonni. An kuma yi amfani da irin wannan manhajar ("StopCovid") a Ireland da Faransa.
Australia da New Zealand duk suna la'akari da aikace-aikacen TraceTogether na Singapore da aikace-aikacen da ke kan yarjejeniyar BlueTrace. Rasha na son gabatar da aikace-aikacen geofencing don marasa lafiya da aka gano da COVID-19 da ke zaune a Moscow, wanda aka tsara don tabbatar da cewa ba sa barin gida.
Ross Anderson, Farfesa a fannin injiniyan tsaro a Jami'ar Cambridge ya lissafa matsaloli masu yawa masu amfani da tsarin tushen aikace-aikace, gami da lokuta masu kuskure da kuma yiwuwar rashin tasiri idan amfani da aikace-aikacen ya iyakance ga karamin yanki na yawan jama'a.
Da yake magance damuwa game da yaduwar aikace-aikacen "coronavirus" masu ɓatarwa ko cutarwa, Apple ya ƙayyade irin nau'ikan ƙungiyoyi da za su iya haɗa da aikace-aikacen da suka shafi coronavirus a cikin App Store, ta hanyar iyakance su ga "hukuma" ko kuma ƙungiyoyi masu daraja kawai.
Google da Amazon sun sanya irin wannan takunkumin.
Masu fafutukar kare sirrin sun nuna damuwarsu game da tasirin sa ido kan mutane ta hanyar amfani da aikace-aikacen coronavirus, musamman game da ko za a lalata kayan aikin sa ido da aka gina don magance cutar coronavirus bayan wannan barazanar ta wuce.
Amnesty International da wasu kungiyoyi sama da 100 sun fitar da wata sanarwa don takaita irin wannan sa ido.
Kungiyoyi sun bayyana sharudda takwas akan ayyukan gwamnati:
Kulawa dole ne ya zama "daidai, dole kuma mai daidaituwa";
Dole ne a sami sashe na ƙarshe don kulawa da kuma tsawo na kulawa;
Amfani da bayanai ya kamata ya zama iyakance ga dalilai na COVID-19;
Dole ne a kiyaye tsaro da rashin sani na bayanai kuma a nuna su a matsayin abin da aka kare bisa ga hujja;
Dole ne kulawar dijital ta guji haɓaka nuna bambanci da hanawa;
Duk wani rabawa na bayanai tare da wasu ɓangarorin uku dole ne a bayyana a cikin doka;
Dole ne a sami matakan kare hakkin 'yan ƙasa don magance cin zarafi da kuma amsawa;
Za a buƙaci "haɗin kai mai ma'ana" daga dukkan "masu ruwa da tsaki masu dacewa", gami da masana kiwon lafiyar jama'a da kungiyoyin marasa iko.
Manufar shirin da aka gabatar na Google / Apple shine magance matsalar sa ido akai -akai ta hanyar cire tsarin sa ido daga tsarin aiki na na'urar su lokacin da ba a buƙatarsa.
Wasu ƙasashe sun yi amfani da bin hanyar sadarwa maimakon aikace -aikace, suna kawar da buƙatar saukar da aikace -aikacen da ikon kauce wa sa ido.
A Isra'ila, an amince da bin hanyar sadarwa.
Hanyoyin sadarwa waɗanda ke da damar yin amfani da bayanan wuri na asali suna da mahimman matsalolin sirri.
Koyaya, ba duk tsarin da ke da sabar tsakiya ba yana buƙatar samun damar bayanan wurin mutum; an ƙirƙiri tsarin tsare sirri da yawa waɗanda ke amfani da sabar tsakiya don sadarwa tare kawai (duba sashe na ƙasa).
An yi amfani da tsarin da ba na aikace -aikace ba don gano lamba a Koriya ta Kudu.
Maimakon amfani da ƙa'idar sadaukarwa, tsarin ya tattara bayanan sa ido daga tushe daban -daban, gami da bayanan sa ido na na'urar hannu da bayanan ma'amala na katin, kuma ya haɗa su don samar da sanarwa ta hanyar saƙonnin rubutu ga mutanen da ke da yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar.
Baya ga amfani da wannan bayanin don faɗakar da masu yuwuwar tuntuɓar, gwamnati ta ba da bayanin wurin a bainar jama'a saboda canje -canje masu nisa a cikin dokokin sirrin bayanai bayan barkewar MERS a wannan ƙasar.
Ana samun wannan bayanin ga jama'a ta hanyar aikace -aikace da rukunin yanar gizo da yawa. Kasashe da yawa, ciki har da Jamus, sun yi la'akari da amfani da tsarin tsakiya da tsare sirri.
Har zuwa 6 ga Afrilu, 2020, ba a fitar da wannan bayanin ba tukuna.
