Koyaya, PEPP-PT ƙoƙari ne na haɗin gwiwa wanda ya haɗa da hanyoyin da aka tsakiya da na rarraba, kuma ba wata yarjejeniya ɗaya ba. Tsarin yarjejeniya ya haɗa da rarraba sirrin sirri-kariya kusa da ganowa (DP-PPT/DP-3T), lambar tuntuɓar wucin gadi (TCN, a baya lambar taron tuntuɓar, CEN), Sirrin Sirri mai mahimmanci da kuma Tsarin don Binciken Sadarwar Sadarwa ta Wayar hannu (PACT) da sauransu.
