Wannan ya dogara ne akan binciken da aka fitar a cikin farar takarda "Aps Gone Rogue: Kula da Sirrin Keɓaɓɓen Sirri a cikin Cutar" a cikin Maris 2020. Irin wannan yunƙurin shine SafeTrace ta Enigma MPC, kamfanin haɓaka fasahar sirri, wanda aka kafa a MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace yana amfani da fasahohin kayan aiki masu aminci, wanda ke ba masu amfani damar raba wuri mai mahimmanci da bayanan kiwon lafiya tare da sauran masu amfani da hukumomi ba tare da yin sulhu kan sirrin wannan bayanan ba.
