Kamar yadda aka bayyana a watan Afrilu, abubuwan da ke da mahimmanci ga shirin CEPI don haɓaka allurar rigakafi sune saurin aiki, ƙarfin samarwa, tsarawa mai yawa da kuma ilmantarwa a duniya.
A watan Afrilu, masana kimiyya a CEPI sun ba da rahoton cewa akwai dandamali daban -daban na fasaha 10 da ke ƙarƙashin bincike da ci gaba a farkon 2020 don ƙirƙirar ingantaccen allurar rigakafi don kariya daga COVID-19.
