Nucleic acid (DNA da RNA) (Mataki na I masu haɓakawa da masu neman allurar rigakafi: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Kwayar cutar (Mataki na I mai haɓaka da mai neman allurar rigakafi: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus type 5 vector)
Kamar yadda masana kimiyya na CEPI suka ruwaito a watan Afrilu, jimillar alluran rigakafi 115 suna cikin matakan farko na ci gaba, daga cikinsu an tabbatar da 78 a matsayin ayyukan aiki (79 a cewar Cibiyar Milken), kuma an sanar da wasu 37, amma akwai karancin bayanan jama'a (wanda ake tsarawa ko kuma ake tsammani a cikin shirin).
A cikin gwajin Mataki na I-II ana gudanar da gwajin farko na aminci da rigakafi, ana yin sa ne a bazuwar, placebo-sarrafawa da wurare da yawa, yawanci ana ƙaddara mafi daidaito, tasiri mai tasiri.
